OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Frain clearing into the evening to give
OL,7,Fplenty of clear spells overnight,
OL,8,Fbecoming cloudy over the Derbyshire
OL,9,Fhills however with the risk of an
OL,10,Fisolated shower. Breezy at times, but
OL,11,Fwinds falling mostly light towards
OL,12,Fdawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FBecoming cloudy through the
OL,15,Fmorning with showers, these will
OL,16,Flikely ease later in the afternoon
OL,17,Fwith sunny spells developing. Clear
OL,18,Fperiods overnight may allow for a
OL,19,Fpatchy frost to develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
